des:
Ask for Aviation Facts, and learn about what huge world of aviation.

Aviation Fun! provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Aviation Fun!" or "Alexa, open Aviation Fun!" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
